&lt;h2 id=&#34;7电磁波传递想法&#34;&gt;7.电磁波传递想法
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;由姜堪政、袁心洲所著，中国医药科技出版社出版的《生物电磁波揭密：场导发现》一书提及微波可以传递想法&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://weiranyi.github.io/p/control-brain/%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E7%94%B5%E7%A3%81%E6%B3%A2%E4%BC%A0%E9%80%92%E6%83%B3%E6%B3%95-%E3%80%8A%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E7%94%B5%E7%A3%81%E6%B3%A2%E6%8F%AD%E5%AF%86%EF%BC%9A%E5%9C%BA%E5%AF%BC%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E3%80%8B.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2878&#34;
	height=&#34;1798&#34;
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;生物电磁波传递想法-《生物电磁波揭密：场导发现》.png&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;160&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;384px&#34;
	
&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;https://weiranyi.github.io/p/control-brain/%E5%8E%9F%E6%96%87%E8%8A%82%E9%80%89-%E3%80%8A%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E7%94%B5%E7%A3%81%E6%B3%A2%E6%8F%AD%E5%AF%86%EF%BC%9A%E5%9C%BA%E5%AF%BC%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E3%80%8B.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2856&#34;
	height=&#34;1482&#34;
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;原文节选-《生物电磁波揭密：场导发现》.png&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;192&#34;
